   <ext_description linkend="Alias_identification_mim.alias_assignment_is_valid">
The <b>alias_assignment_is_valid</b> function evaluates whether an instance of <express_ref linkend="identification_assignment:mim:Identification_assignment_mim.applied_identification_assignment"/>

 whose identification role is 'alias',
contains, in its items attribute, only instances of types listed in <express_ref linkend="alias_identification:mim:Alias_identification_mim.aliasable_item"/>.
<p>The function returns TRUE is the role is not 'alias' or if the items attribute only contains instances of types listed in <express_ref linkend="alias_identification:mim:Alias_identification_mim.aliasable_item"/>.
</p></ext_description>

   <ext_description linkend="Alias_identification_mim.alias_assignment_is_valid.aia">
the instance of <express_ref linkend="identification_assignment:mim:Identification_assignment_mim.applied_identification_assignment"/>, the validity of which is assessed.
</ext_description>

